data.description: This stunning 5-bedroom, 3-full bath plus bonus room home is located in the Holden Creek Preserve subdivision, a delightful pool community justmoments away from downtown Youngsville. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the charm of a young home that has been meticulously maintained. Themain floor offers a guest bedroom with an adjacent full bath, offering convenience and flexibility for your living needs. Enjoy newer bamboo flooring andbrand new carpet. Entertain effortlessly in the family room featuring built-ins and a cozy gas fireplace. The kitchen is a dream with a large center island,granite counters, stainless appliances - including a gas range - and a pantry. The adjacent breakfast area is bathed in natural light, creating the perfect spotfor your morning coffee. For more formal occasions, the dining room is adorned with shiplap, adding a touch of character to your dining experience.Stepoutside to a large screened porch overlooking a large, fully fenced yard. Whether you're hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet evenings, this outdoor space isa true retreat. Venture to the second floor where you'll find four additional bedrooms, a pass-through laundry room equipped with newer washer and dryer,and a bonus room that offers endless possibilities. The spacious primary bedroom suite is a sanctuary with two walk-in closets featuring solid shelving, adouble vanity, and a tiled shower. Convenience meets recreation with the property located just one block from the community pool and playground.
